### Test Deployed Backend Endpoints
### Base URL: https://resume-skill-clustering.vercel.app

### 1. Health Check
GET https://resume-skill-clustering.vercel.app/health

### 2. Dataset Info
GET https://resume-skill-clustering.vercel.app/dataset-info

### 3. Cluster Distribution
GET https://resume-skill-clustering.vercel.app/cluster-distribution

### 4. Analyze Text
POST https://resume-skill-clustering.vercel.app/analyze-text
Content-Type: application/json
{
  "text": "Sample resume text for testing"
}

### 5. Analyze File
POST https://resume-skill-clustering.vercel.app/analyze-file
Content-Type: multipart/form-data

### 6. PCA Visualization
POST https://resume-skill-clustering.vercel.app/pca-visualization
Content-Type: application/json
{
  "text": "Sample resume text for testing"
}

### 7. Clusters Visualization
GET https://resume-skill-clustering.vercel.app/clusters-visualization

### Environment Variables
- PYTHON_VERSION: 3.9
